---
title: Miso Ginger Barramundi with Chili-Garlic Roasted Zucchini & Carrots
description: Simple, flavorful, colorful, and filling? It may seem fishy, but there’s no catch—this miso ginger barramundi is a straight-up weeknight winner! The delicate fish is seared and then coated in a gingery sauce infused with umami-rich miso paste, the deeply savory Japanese ingredient. On the side, roasted carrots and zucchini are tossed with a chili garlic oil for a hint of heat, rounding the plate for a surprisingly simple dinner victory!
